        {
            "id": "urn:newsml:mtnewswires.com:20250206:G2464381:0",
            "title": "Fitch Affirms Multitude Rating with Positive Outlook on Improving Profitability",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><span><p class=\"\">Fitch Ratings affirmed its long-term issuer default rating of B+ for Multitude  with a positive outlook on Wednesday. </p><p class=\"\">The rating agency said that the outlook reflects the financial technology company's improving business volumes and profitability as well as adequate capitalization. </p><p class=\"\">Fitch noted that the company's rating is constrained due to its niche franchise in high-yield consumer and small- and medium-enterprise lending and pressure on its net interest margin.</p></span></div>",
